g r\u1ed3i cho x\u1ea3 b\u0103m nh\u1ecf v\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec1u.<\/li>\n<li>L\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t cho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ecfi b\u0103m, h\u00e0nh b\u0103m, g\u1eebng b\u0103m, \u1edbt b\u0103m v\u00e0o, tr\u1ed9n \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u01a1m. Sau \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed5 \u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 lu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p tr\u00ean.<\/li>\n<li>N\u00eam gia v\u1ecb g\u1ed3m \u00bd th\u00eca canh \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u00bc th\u00eca canh h\u1ea1t ti\u00eau xay, 1 th\u00eca n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eafm, \u00bd th\u00eca sa t\u1ebf v\u00e0o r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3ng 2 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed1c th\u1ea5m gia v\u1ecb.<\/li>\n<li>Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng cho rau b\u0103m v\u00e0o l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh. Cho \u1ed1c ra d\u0129a r\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c khi c\u00f2n n\u00f3ng th\u00f4i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>\u1ed0c h\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea5p s\u1ea3<\/strong><\/h2>\n<h4><strong>Nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ed0c h\u01b0\u01a1ng, s\u1ea3 \u0111\u1eadp d\u1eadp, gia v\u1ecb<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2835 size-full litespeed-loaded\" src=\"http:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19.jpg 600w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19-248x248.jpg 248w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19-150x150.jpg 150w\" alt=\"\u1ed0c h\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1ea5p s\u1ea3\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazyloaded=\"1\" data-src=\"http:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-19.jp