0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i ghi\u1ec1n m\u00f3n n\u00e0y, h\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n<h4><strong>Nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\u1ed0c h\u01b0\u01a1ng, gia v\u1ecb<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2823 size-full litespeed-loaded\" src=\"http:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7.jpg 600w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-248x248.jpg 248w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-150x150.jpg 150w\" alt=\"\u1ed0c h\u01b0\u01a1ng rang mu\u1ed1i\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" data-lazyloaded=\"1\" data-src=\"http:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7.jpg 600w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-248x248.jpg 248w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/haisanmrd.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/Oc-Huong-7-150x150.jpg 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u1ed0c h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n ngon \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, d\u1ec5 l\u00e0m T\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u1ed1c h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u